WEBVTT

00:02.000 --> 00:05.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: President Trump's
use of Twitter has often brought
praise from supporters for

00:05.533 --> 00:08.266 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
reaching out directly
to the American people.

00:08.266 --> 00:13.266 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
