00:19.166 --> 00:22.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
MIKA BRZEZINSKI,
Co-Host, "Morning Joe":
President Donald Trump.

00:22.166 --> 00:27.166 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
