a firestorm, even from
his Republican allies.

01:01.200 --> 01:03.666 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

01:03.666 --> 01:04.333 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LINDSEY GRAHAM (R),
South Carolina: I thought
it was inappropriate,
beneath the office,

01:04.333 --> 01:06.233 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
