01:06.233 --> 01:07.733 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

01:07.733 --> 01:08.266 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
ORRIN HATCH (R), Utah: I wish,
I wish he hadn't made the tweet.

01:08.266 --> 01:10.366 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
REP.

01:10.366 --> 01:12.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
PAUL RYAN (R-WI), Speaker of
the House: I don't see that
as an appropriate comment.

01:12.400 --> 01:15.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I think, look, what we're trying
to do around here is improve
tone, the civility of debates.

01:15.866 --> 01:17.933 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
