reaction to that?

01:24.633 --> 01:26.133 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

01:26.133 --> 01:27.066 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
SHELLEY MOORE CAPITO (R),
West Virginia: Distasteful.

01:27.066 --> 01:27.600 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: And from Democrats.

01:27.600 --> 01:29.566 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
REP.

01:29.566 --> 01:31.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
BRENDA LAWRENCE (D),
