02:53.600 --> 02:55.466 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
cable television hosts.

02:55.466 --> 02:57.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
For the "PBS NewsHour,"
