of the office.

07:45.933 --> 07:50.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Matt Dowd,
clearly this was part and parcel
of the president lashing out

07:50.400 --> 07:52.866 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
