president -- in any way
does this further the
agenda of the president?

08:06.000 --> 08:11.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
You mentioned a minute ago
his health care plan, the fact
that he is trying to get this

08:12.966 --> 08:16.100 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
health care plan through the
Senate, through the Congress,
and this takes all the attention

08:16.100 --> 08:18.200 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
away from that.

08:18.200 --> 08:22.300 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
MATTHEW DOWD: Well, I
think attributing any
every time somebody --
Donald Trump does this,

08:23.900 --> 08:25.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
President Trump does
this, people attribute
some grand strategy.

08:25.833 --> 08:28.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
