08:47.533 --> 08:51.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
You can't argue any otherwise
in the midst of this, a woman
who serves as an anchor on

08:51.333 --> 08:52.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
a television program.

08:52.900 --> 08:55.266 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
